%BLUE% *minutes:*

As of today's telecon, only Action Item 5 and 11 are still outstanding. Bill Johnston has informed the council co-chairs that he will not be able to attend the Face-to-Face meeting to report on 11 as originally planned last August. There is a session on VM technology on the agenda for the All-Hands-Meeting which will hopefully make some progress on this subject. Doug asked if Magellan would be at, or could be at the session to present.

